From 8e2e9312ab4d53d15046fdc8b4a442fefb65434f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 00:00:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/5] PDP v10: rebuild inline review slider to mockup .prf card

- Header row: static 5-star summary + bordered square prev/next arrows
- Italic quote, name+flag+role, verified tag, B2B badge support
- Footer: bar dots + 'Read all reviews' link (block setting)
- Brand tokens (sage/emerald) + Clash Grotesk/DM Sans, 8px radius
- Enable inline slider via section toggle, placed under the trust rows
- Mobile-first with 768px desktop refinement for the sticky right column
